desc: Get ready for the next generation of sustainable farming. Here at Victory Farms, we're committed to providing the freshest, best tasting produce to our community. We're adopting the 40 year legacy of Don Kretschmann's Organic Farm, empowering us to deliver the healthiest food greater Pittsburgh could ask for.

layout.text: Better Food Makes for a Better Life
We're taking health into our own hands and sharing it with all Greater Pittsburgh!
